Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties

data.description: Nestled within the heart of one of Wilmington's earliest neighborhoods, Sunset Park, lies a charming bungalow with warmth and character - and off street parking! Located a short distance from the vibrant South Front District of Downtown, serene Greenfield Lake, and sporting events at Legion Stadium.Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the inviting embrace of a well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1-bath haven. The home was renovated in 2017 including new roof and central Heating and Air- conditioning system and it also has new interior paint! The spacious living room, adorned with original hardwood floors, sets the tone for comfort and coziness. An open kitchen invites culinary adventures, creating a seamless flow into the dining room, where shared meals become cherished moments.Hardwood floors guide you through the home, leading to the tiled bathroom--a touch of modernity amidst classic charm. Venture outside to discover a covered porch, its pull-down screen transforming it into a sanctuary for al fresco summer movie nights.The yard also has a practical shed, offering storage solutions for the everyday items that make a house a home. The former concrete- block built garage can potentially have new roof framing added to recreate a workshop or secure parking for vehicles, or for a workshop or studio space. Additionally, a firepit area promises evenings of shared stories and warmth under the stars.Reach out, schedule a viewing, and make it yours.
